Label: diphosphate synthase
Comment: Catalyzes the conversion of geranyl-PP into trans,trans-farnesyl diphosphate.

Label: 1-carboxyvinyltransferase
Comment: Facilitates the conversion of trans,trans-farnesyl diphosphate to geranylgeranyl diphosphate.

Label: dimethylallyltranstransferase
Comment: Facilitates the conversion of dimethylallyl-PP to geranyl-PP.
